the loathsome nickname,</i>

249
00:16:20,828 --> 00:16:25,188
<i>we went to Wiz's shop to discuss
settling the debt.</i>

250
00:16:25,467 --> 00:16:28,547
I am sorry, can we sell this here?

251
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:33,240
-This is...
-I am Yunyun.

252
00:16:33,316 --> 00:16:36,736
What a coincidence!
This must be fate's planning.

253
00:16:36,956 --> 00:16:40,676
We actually meet each other here.
We really are rivals.

254
00:16:41,244 --> 00:16:45,684
She's been waiting the whole morning
after I told her you often come here.

255
00:16:45,756 --> 00:16:47,956
What are you talking about, lady boss?

256
00:16:48,051 --> 00:16:50,611
I am just here to buy magical equipment.

257
00:16:50,688 --> 00:16:53,880
Please, I want to buy this.

258
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:56,544
I see.

259
00:16:56,680 --> 00:17:00,080
You don't have to take a detour.
Just come straight to our house.

260
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:03,640
I can't go to other's house so suddenly.

261
00:17:03,744 --> 00:17:06,656
You deserve to be alone
for being so whiny.

262
00:17:06,848 --> 00:17:07,904
Really?

263
00:17:07,996 --> 00:17:11,276
Yunyun is a freak.
She thinks her name invites mockery.

264
00:17:11,556 --> 00:17:14,516
She always ate her lunch alone in school.

265
00:17:14,916 --> 00:17:17,756
I purposely used petty moves on her,

266
00:17:17,876 --> 00:17:20,796
but she still came here all
cheered up for a fight.

267
00:17:20,916 --> 00:17:24,236
It's not as bad as you said.
I do have friends.

268
00:17:24,516 --> 00:17:28,196
I heard the keyword. You have a friend?

269
00:17:28,356 --> 00:17:30,876
Yes, I have friends and they are real.

270
00:17:31,116 --> 00:17:34,476
Funifura and Dodonko are both my friends.

271
00:17:34,587 --> 00:17:37,108
Then I bought both of them a meal.

272
00:17:37,276 --> 00:17:40,116
That's enough,
we don't want to hear anything more.

273
00:17:40,276 --> 00:17:43,456
I can only use explosion spells.

274
00:17:43,584 --> 00:17:46,032
I would rather avoid any magical battle.

275
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:48,540
You can always learn other magic.

276
00:17:48,676 --> 00:17:51,036
I am sure you earned
a lot of skill points.

277
00:17:51,139 --> 00:17:52,419
I did earn a lot.

278
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:56,240
I spent them all on
upgrading explosion magic...

279
00:17:56,316 --> 00:17:58,356
and high-speed incantations.

280
00:17:58,436 --> 00:18:01,596
Fool, why are you so obsessed
with explosion spells?

281
00:18:01,676 --> 00:18:03,556
Sure, keep her talking.

282
00:18:03,636 --> 00:18:05,206
She is always so stubborn.

283
00:18:05,316 --> 00:18:08,436
Duel, duel, duel. They are schoolmates,
yet she is so bloodthirsty.

284
00:18:08,768 --> 00:18:09,824
Hey!

285
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:13,800
This can be useful.
The Crystal of Friendship.

286
00:18:14,116 --> 00:18:17,356
If a magician doesn't have
the required skill,

287
00:18:17,472 --> 00:18:19,048
she can't use this item to its fullest.

288
00:18:19,236 --> 00:18:22,276
Can I make new friends
if I use it properly?

289
00:18:22,476 --> 00:18:23,716
Yes.

290
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:26,160
Okay, let's try it out.

291
00:18:26,276 --> 00:18:29,476
There is no reason for us
to be good friends.

292
00:18:29,596 --> 00:18:31,436
Are you afraid, Megumin?

293
00:18:32,036 --> 00:18:33,147
In other words,

294
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:37,040
any who can use it correctly
is the better magician.

295
00:18:37,459 --> 00:18:38,979
Megumin, let's duel!

296
00:18:39,259 --> 00:18:42,234
If you say so, I will have to show you...

297
00:18:42,476 --> 00:18:44,876
the power of a true magician!

298
00:18:44,996 --> 00:18:47,556
Let's settle it once and for all today!

299
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:54,480
Crimson Magic Clan sure is impressive.

300
00:18:54,586 --> 00:18:57,596
Crystal, show me your power!

301
00:18:57,691 --> 00:19:00,131
The crystal's energy is activating.

302
00:19:08,076 --> 00:19:10,556
I have never seen so
many projections at once before.

303
00:19:10,686 --> 00:19:12,246
They are both amazing.

304
00:19:12,427 --> 00:19:14,827
What is this?

305
00:19:22,316 --> 00:19:24,636
She is collecting bread crust.

306
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,880
Wait.

307
00:19:31,179 --> 00:19:32,299
Happy Birthday!

308
00:19:34,756 --> 00:19:36,676
She was all alone?

309
00:19:36,840 --> 00:19:38,280
Stop!

310
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:41,760
Big Sister, you are awesome!

311
00:19:47,716 --> 00:19:49,636
Not bad, how about this move?

312
00:19:52,676 --> 00:19:55,076
You are amazing!

313
00:20:04,676 --> 00:20:07,076
Big Sister, you are awesome!

314
00:20:07,756 --> 00:20:10,516
Making friends with a demon
is not bad, either.

315
00:20:10,836 --> 00:20:14,476
She worked odd jobs just
to buy her friends a meal?

316
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:18,120
What is that? They are eating bugs.

317
00:20:19,916 --> 00:20:21,076
What is this thing?

318
00:20:21,196 --> 00:20:23,916
Lady boss, I thought you say
this is the Crystal of Friendship.

319
00:20:23,996 --> 00:20:27,596
This is a value-for-money item

320
00:20:27,676 --> 00:20:30,036
that improves relationships...

321
00:20:30,116 --> 00:20:34,219
by showing each other your darkest past.

322
00:20:34,716 --> 00:20:38,476
Megumin, can we be friends?

323
00:20:38,596 --> 00:20:41,519
Here it goes!

324
00:20:47,436 --> 00:20:49,836
I will put this in Kazuma's bill.

325
00:20:49,956 --> 00:20:52,556
Wait, Megumin is the one who broke it.

326
00:20:52,756 --> 00:20:56,636
Yunyun wanted to use that item.
She should pay the bill.

327
00:20:56,716 --> 00:20:59,036
A duel. A memorable duel.

328
00:20:59,116 --> 00:21:00,824
When are you going to stop sobbing?

329
00:21:00,956 --> 00:21:03,904
But in the end, we can't tell
who the winner is.

330
00:21:04,036 --> 00:21:05,673
Can we make this a draw?

331
00:21:05,916 --> 00:21:07,636
I am fine with that.

332
00:21:08,276 --> 00:21:11,716
I am not a kid who will
grudge against this kind of thing.

333
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:16,400
Right, we once promised to see
who grew up faster.

334
00:21:16,516 --> 00:21:19,956
Since you said you are not a kid,
we can have a match on that.

335
00:21:20,076 --> 00:21:24,516
When I said I am not a kid,
I meant something else.

336
00:21:25,076 --> 00:21:27,236
That's because...

337
00:21:30,320 --> 00:21:34,400
I am so close to Kazuma that
we even shared the same bath.

338
00:21:34,476 --> 00:21:36,236
-Wait!
-What?

339
00:21:39,556 --> 00:21:40,836
What are you talking about?

340
00:21:40,956 --> 00:21:43,996
This big mouth of yours!
Are you trying to spread rumors with it?

341
00:21:44,332 --> 00:21:45,979
Today...

342
00:21:46,436 --> 00:21:50,276
Today, I have completely lost to her!

343
00:21:51,659 --> 00:21:52,928
Please, come again!

344
00:21:53,036 --> 00:21:54,436
What a bothersome kid.

345
00:21:54,567 --> 00:21:55,687
Speak of yourself.

346
00:21:58,476 --> 00:21:59,699
Another victory today!

347
00:23:30,016 --> 00:23:39,925
(Episode 3:
Peace for the Master of This Labyrinth!)

